              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": "left"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It supports functional and structured programming methods as well as OOP."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": "left"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It can be used as a scripting language or can be compiled to byte-code for building large applications."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": "left"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It provides very high-level dynamic data types and supports dynamic type checking."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": "left"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It supports automatic garbage collection."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "attrs": {
                "textAlign": "left"
              },
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "It can be easily integrated with C, C++, COM, ActiveX, CORBA, and Java."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
